description: Something happened to these kaomojis, something they’re not thrilled about and they’re thinking something like “seriously?” or “really?”. This is how I feel every time I find another site or app that copied everything they have from this site. Sigh. I’m sure you find yourself thinking about something you’re not thrilled about sometimes. If you catch yourself doing it, try to redirect your thoughts to something positive about the situation.
